        },
        {
            "title": "財經｜正榮地產(06158)料去年虧損擴至逾170億人民幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜正榮地產(06158)料去年虧損擴至逾170億人民幣\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜正榮地產(06158)料去年虧損擴至逾170億人民幣</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">正榮地產(06158)發盈警，預計截至2025年12月底止年度股東應佔虧損約170億至180億元(人民幣．下同)，2024年度虧損約68.3億元；去年度的核心虧損料約50億至約60億元，2024年度則約31.78億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司稱，股東應佔虧損主要源於去年隨着內地房地產行業整體需求下滑，造成項目售價及毛利下降以及開發中物業、持作出售已竣工物業及其他資產以及金融資產相關減值撥備；未資本化的融資利息增加；及投資物業公平值下降。預期虧損將會增加，主要由於對比2024年度，2025年度毛利減少及減值虧損撥備增加所致。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E6%AD%A3%E6%A6%AE%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2-06158-%E6%96%99%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E8%99%A7%E6%90%8D%E6%93%B4%E8%87%B3%E9%80%BE170%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3-065043216.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-20 15:02:03",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "小米狂瀉7%股價接近腰斬！SU7保守定價利潤「亞歷山大」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周五，3月20日，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"小米集團\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:小米集團;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/小米集團\">小米集團</a>－Ｗ (HK:1810)重挫近7%，自去年高點以來，股價接近腰斬。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息面上，3月19日晚，小米汽車召開新一代SU7-小米春季新品發佈會，主題為「人車家全生態全面落地」，新一代SU7、Xiaomi Book Pro 14、Xiaomi Watch S5三大新品集中亮相。新一代小米SU7僅材料成本就增加了小2萬元，但在定價上，新一代SU7只升了4000元，起售價21.99萬元。雷軍還宣佈，未來三年，小米在AI領域的投入將超過600億元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-57658445-ac67-3214-8659-f04314f0442c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">值得關注的是，3月18日小米集團斥資近1億港元回購285.04萬股，回購均價35.08港元。年內累計回購金額已達45.77億港元，僅次於騰訊控股，管理層逆市增持彰顯對公司長期發展的信心。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據InvestingPro顯示，小米集團的公允價值為43.84港元，存在29.2%的上升空間。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"749\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rcB6GAFRyVdtUKt.97IAsQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc0OQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/e7eb1e3b2e96a492016340b27a64001e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"undefined\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:undefined;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">undefined</a></p></div>",
